{"type": "article", "id": 49993, "title": "有一把木头菜刀，估计你会说不实用｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-02-06T23:04:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 5579, "name": "Snøhetta"}, {"id": 47623, "name": "AteljéLyktan"}, {"id": 47624, "name": "The Rug Company"}, {"id": 47625, "name": "Bonnemazou-Cambus"}, {"id": 47626, "name": "Elements-S"}, {"id": 47627, "name": "5th Column"}, {"id": 47628, "name": "Maison Milan"}, {"id": 17876, "name": "Sebastian Herkner"}, {"id": 47629, "name": "Armando Bruno"}, {"id": 47630, "name": "Chifen Cheng"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 136, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180207070352LUrsGiHDcpYxjEuO.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s9 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The knife Reinvented by  Chifen Cheng for Maison Milan</h3><p>意大利设计品牌 Maison Milan 推出了一款创新刀具，邀请了出生自台湾的加拿大产品设计师 Chifen Cheng 之手。她常关注日常用品，比如这次就选择着手改造传统灯具，刀片由坚实的核桃木片制作而成，而它的铸铁手柄则可以用于研磨香料或者胡椒等。</p><p>大多数金属刀具在切菜的时候，蔬菜会出现变色的问题，但核桃木材料不会出现这个问题。更重要的是，它易于抓握，较为安全，即使是小朋友使用也不会太过担心。售价 90 美元，<a href=\"http://milandesign.co/en/shop/knife-reinvented/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214436ifKuZ9sNV2vdPy4k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214436nAS48w9LkBvtlIhX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.856445\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214436xNGLWBpsd4lwjhy1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214436op7SJQcCYsMeRqVX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214436x29BAdLUDT5shZ7J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://milandesign.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">milandesign.co</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>One to One Geometric Mirror Collection by Armando Bruno</h3><p>来自米兰的室内设计师 Armando Bruno 会在今年 4 月的米兰设计周推出他的 One to One 镜子系列，每个镜子以不同形状、独特数码印制的云石条纹和图案，利用镜子有限的空间创作出富有简约时尚的单品。</p><p>这个系列包括圆形、六边形、三角形和长方形，不重复的大理石花纹，归功于将技术和工艺相结合的生产工艺。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214540onWEtBfUSsXLecCY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214540fhRuntw9SHLUomYF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214540Iuvz7L6A2FZip84M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214541ZX4hWH1AVKRkqtEI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214541GrBU8Eef0P3ZC9td.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214542bHheWwyYrLjqGfRC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/one-to-one-geometric-mirror-collection-by-armando-bruno/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designmilk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Ciro Wooden Stool by 5th Column</h3><p>5th Column 是印度瓦尔道拉一家建筑、室内及家具设计咨询公司。Ciro 是一款融合了现代和传统生产工艺，经过一系列不同材料实验出来的凳子。它的主体由木材制成，并结合了铝制框架。在如今大规模生产的大环境下，5th Column 希望能够复兴传统手工制品，关注细节及其设计背后的故事。</p><p>虽然凳子的框架是铸铝，座椅是机器制造木材，但连接这些部分的是手工编织甘蔗，赋予座垫弹性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018020621462576EIRmdoPaz0iksj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214625ygGvQHLFNS3i4acT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214625b2iFy6RWnCtm3aks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214625QMHU1zAtDVhvj5Ig.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214628GMTjic1xZrt7ORPN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.905000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://fifthcolumn.in/?portfolio_page=ciro-a-wooden-stool\" rel=\"nofollow\">5th Column</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Modern Door Hardware by Elements-S for <span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bonnemazou-Cambus</span></h3><p>你可能很少注意到门把手的设计细节，但看看法国品牌 <a href=\"http://www.bonnemazou-cambus.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bonnemazou-Cambus</a> 推出的门把手，你可能会产生兴趣。</p><p>2014 年，两位巴黎设计师 AgnèsCambus 和 Manuel Bonnemazou 成立了创意工作室 Elements-S，专门设计各种装饰门的配件，可与不同的门板配合使用。许多门把手使用黄铜材质，刻意留下清漆饰面的自然脱落痕迹，随着时间可以发展出独特的复古色调。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214720cmFHQLVa9UlCYjwO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214720aoJhuvA7ejX1RlsD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214720LPF1mtE8MlHV0gUG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214720Zm148kPbDIrBnC3w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214720qEMCxeuK6g7PVr5D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.bonnemazou-cambus.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bonnemazou-Cambus</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>A City-Inspired Rug Collection by Sebastian Herkner for The Rug Company</h3><p>德国设计师 Sebastian Herkner 为地毯公司 The Rug Company 设计的城市灵感地毯，于 1 月份的科隆国际家具展首次亮相。城市灵感系列包括两种设计： Mainland Dark 和 Mainland Light，灵感来自充满交叉路口、道路、移动车辆和空旷空间的城市景观。</p><p>这两种设计均采用丝绒和西藏羊毛的混合物，以不同的绒面高度在四个相交的纹理上制成，给人以立体的感觉。每个地毯都是由尼泊尔熟练的工匠手工打结，使用机器无法复制的传统编织技术制成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214805fL4Jnucv9Tgjo62V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687654\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214805H21swvDE6G4i9foM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802062148054eUVQCjJFzfWmA8y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214805Jy9zGeK673bWjwhB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214805xiXEMBvsUG8LkDH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498438\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/mainland-a-city-inspired-rug-collection-by-sebastian-herkner-for-the-rug-company/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designmilk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Flik Flak Collection by Snøhetta for AteljéLyktan</h3><p>挪威建筑事务所 Snøhetta 创造了一系列铰接的木质灯具 Flik Flak，最初是为瑞典 Treehotel 的树顶小屋设计的。这个系列于本周的斯德哥尔摩设计周上亮相，包括壁灯、台灯和落地灯。</p><p>这是 Snøhetta 首次涉足照明设备设计领域，是受瑞典品牌 AteljéLyktan 之邀设计。Flik Flak 系列试图体现建筑物的外观，由夹在两片黑色桦木贴面之间的 LED 灯条制成。木板通过钢琴铰链固定在一起，使灯能以 180 度的角度打开和关闭。关闭时，光线集中在一个区域，打开时则分散在整个空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214858aHhFgz4I0u8bsYPR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749577\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214858LTPMfibqSj9NumnF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214858EDA3YwkCifzmBJ1X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692470\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214859dqIgwRThmBpG74Y9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214858J54MeraHdYpyWUCO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180206214859zHPxal26swXLFpGK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/02/05/snohetta-unveils-first-ever-lighting-collection-atelje-lyktan-stockholm-design-week/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}